## Verification checklist

- Card database remains exactly as documented.
- Prices, destinations, limits, and market pools match PRD.
- Income order and formula match PRD.
- Price modifier order is exact.
- Market generation is deterministic and uses unified random.
- Purchase and rebuild are mutation-safe.
- Role effects apply only to the human player.
- Role flags are consumed only on success.
- UI does not own economy or card behavior.
- No Resource display text is parsed as gameplay logic.
- Required GUT coverage exists or was updated.
